text: Rungrath Poomchantuek (, born May 17, 1992), simply known as Prince () is a Thai professional footballer who plays as a Winger for Thai League 1 club Ratchaburi Mitr Phol and the Thailand national team. ==International career== In March, 2015 Rungrath debut for Thailand in a friendly match against Singapore.
